title: Tempest (01 - 04) (1996 - 1997) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire)
description:
Tempest (01 - 04) (1996 - 1997) (Digital) (BlackManta-Empire)


4 issue mini-series written and drawn by Phil Jimenez spinning out of Peter David's popular Aquaman (1994) series.  
 
Garth had been a regular cast member as Aqualad but had gone off to train with the wizard Atlan. During the events of the mini-series Garth and Atlan are trapped in a neather realm where upon he claims his birth right as The Tempest, battles the evil Slizzath and must confront a projection of his dead lover Tula.
